<html><head><style>body{font-family:'Segoe UI', Calibri, sans-serif; line-height:1.6;} h1{color:#2E4053; border-bottom:2px solid #2E4053;} h2{color:#2874A6;} code{background:#F4F6F6; padding:2px; font-family:Consolas, monospace;}</style></head><body><h1>HTML Template: forgot_password.html</h1>
<h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>
<p>Defines the structural layout and content for a specific web page view.</p>
<h2>2. Code Logic &amp; Functionality</h2>
<p>Uses the Jinja2 templating engine. The file allows for dynamic data insertion using <code>{{ variable }}</code> syntax and control structures like <code>{% if %}</code> loops within standard HTML markup.</p>
<h2>3. Key Concepts &amp; Definitions</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Jinja2</strong>: A modern and designer-friendly templating language for Python.</li>
<li><strong>Template Inheritance</strong>: The ability to extend a base layout (<code>base.html</code>) to avoid code duplication.</li>
<li><strong>DOM</strong>: Document Object Model, the data representation of the objects that comprise the structure and content of a document on the web.</li>
</ul>
<h2>4. Location Details</h2>
<p><strong>Path</strong>: <code>templates\forgot_password.html</code>
<strong>Type</strong>: .HTML File</p>
<h2>5. Source Code Preview (Snippet)</h2>
<p>Running typical software analysis on this file:</p>
<p>```html
{% extends "base.html" %}</p>
<p>{% block title %}Forgot Password - Greenwood International{% endblock %}</p>
<p>{% block content %}</p>
<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
                <div class="card-body p-5">
                    <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <div class="rounded-circle bg-light d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3"
                            style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                            <i class="fas fa-lock text-primary fa-2x"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="card-title fw-bold text-primary">Forgot Password?</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted small">Enter your email address and we'll send you a link to reset your
                            password.</p>
                    </div>

                    {% with messages = get_flashed_messages(with_categories=true) %}
                    {% if messages %}
                    {% for category, message in messages %}
                    <div class="alert alert-{{ category }} alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                        {{ message }}
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                    {% endif %}
                    {% endwith %}

                    <form method="POST" action="{{ url_for('forgot_password') }}">
                        <input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token() }}" />

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label for="email" class="form-label fw-bold text-primary">Email Address</label>
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-text bg-light border-end-0"><i
                                        class="fas fa-envelope text-muted"></i></span>
                                <input type="email" class="form-control form-control-lg border-start-0 ps-0" id="email"
                                    name="email" placeholder="name@example.com" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary-custom btn-lg w-100 mb-3">Send Reset Link</button>
                    </form>

                    <div class="text-center mt-4">
                        <a href="{{ url_for('login') }}" class="text-decoration-none fw-bold text-muted small">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-1"></i> Back to Login
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<p>{% endblock %}
```</p></body></html>